hy pRBU! ijs mnu`K nUM qUM (Awqmk AwnMd dI dwiq) dyNdw hYN auh pRwpq krdw hY[
auhI mnu`K (ies dwq nUM) mwxdw hY ijs nUM qUM idMdw hYN, hornW ivcwirAW dI (mwieAw dy hVH A`gy) koeI pyS nhIN jWdI[
keI bMdy (mwieAw dI) Btkxw ivc (Asl rsqy qoN) Bu`ly hoey dsIN pwsIN dOVdy iPrdy hn, keI (BwgW vwilAW nUM) qUM Awpxy nwm ivc joV ky (auhnW dw jnm) svwr dyNdw hYN[
(ies qrHW qyrI myhr nwl) ijn@W nUM qyrI rzw ipAwrI l`gx l`g pYNdI hY, gurU dI ikrpw nwl auhnW dw mn pivqR ho jWdw hY (qy auh Awqmk AwnMd mwxdy hn,
(pr) nwnk AwKdw hY ik (hy pRBU!) ijs nUM qUM (Awqmk AwnMd dI dwiq) b^Sdw hYN auhI ies nUM mwx skdw hY ]8]
hy ipAwry sMq jno! AwE, AsIN (rl ky) byAMq guxW vwly prmwqmw dIAW is&q-swlwh dIAW g`lW krIey,
aus pRBU dIAW khwxIAW suxIey suxweIey ijs dy gux ibAwn qoN pry hn[ (pr jy qusI pu`Co ik) auh pRBU iks qrIky nwl imldw hY?
(qW au~qr ieh hY ik Awpxw Awp mwieAw dy hvwly krn dy QW) Awpxw qn mn Dn sB kuJ gurU dy hvwly kro (ies qrHW) jy gurU dw hukm im`Tw l`gx l`g pey qW prmwqmw iml pYNdw hY[
(so, sMq jno!) gurU dy hukm au~qy quro qy sdw kwiem rihx vwly pRBU dI is&q-swlwh dI bwxI gwieAw kro[
nwnk AwKdw hY ik hy sMq jno suxo, (aus nUM imlx dw Aqy Awqmk AwnMd mwxn dw shI rsqw iehI hY ik) aus Ak`Q pRBU dIAW khwxIAW kirAw kro ]9]
hy cMcl mn! clwkIAW nwl iksy ny BI (Awqmk AwnMd) hwsl nhIN kIqw[
hy myry mn! qUM (iDAwn nwl) sux lY ik iksy jIv ny BI cqurweI nwl (prmwqmw dy imlwp dw AwnMd) pRwpq nhIN kIqw[
(AMdroN mohxI mwieAw ivc BI PisAw rhy, qy, bwhroN inrIAW g`lW nwl Awqmk AwnMd cwhy, ieh nhIN ho skdw)[ ieh mwieAw jIvW nUM Awpxy moh ivc Pswx leI bVI fwFI hY, ies ny ies BulyKy ivc pwieAw hoieAw hY ik moh im`TI cIz hY, ies qrHW kurwhy pweI r`KdI hY[
(pr jIv dy BI kIh v`s?) ijs pRBU ny mwieAw dy moh dI TgbUtI (jIvW nUM) cMboVI hY ausy ny ieh mohxI mwieAw pYdw kIqI hY[
(so, hy myry mn! Awpxy Awp nUM mwieAw qoN sdky krn dy QW) aus pRBU qoN hI sdky kro ijs ny im`Tw moh lwieAw hY (qdoN hI ieh im`Tw moh mu`kdw hY)[
nwnk AwKdw hY ik hy (myry) cMcl mn! cqurweIAW nwl iksy ny (prmwqmw dy imlwp dw Awqmk AwnMd) nhIN l`Bw ]10]
hy ipAwry mn! (jy qUM sdw dw Awqmk AwnMd loVdw hYN qW) sdw s`cy pRBU nUM (Awpxy AMdr) sMBwl r`K!
ieh jyhVw prvwr qUM vyKdw hYN, ies ny qyry nwl nhIN inBxw[
ies prvwr dy moh ivc ikauN Psdw hYN? ies ny qyry nwl qoV sdw dw swQ nhIN inbwh skxw[
ijs kMm dy kIiqAW Aw^r h`Q mlxy pYx, auh kMm kdy BI krnw nhIN cwhIdw[
siqgurU dI is`iKAw (ghu nwl) sux, ieh gur-aupdyS sdw cyqy r`Kxw cwhIdw hY[
nwnk AwKdw hY ik hy ipAwry mn! (jy qUM AwnMd loVdw hYN qW) sdw-iQr prmwqmw nUM hr vyly (Awpxy AMdr) sWB ky r`K ]11]
(hy ipAwry mn! sdw pRBU nUM Awpxy AMdr sMBwl r`K, qy aus dy A`gy ieauN ArzoeI kr-) hy AphuMc hrI! hy ieMidRAW dI phuMc qoN pry rihx vwly pRBU! (qyry guxW dw) iksy ny AMq nhIN l`Bw[
Awpxy (Asl) srUp nUM qUM Awp hI jwxdw hYN, hor koeI jIv qyry guxW dw A^Ir nhIN l`B skdw[
koeI hor jIv (qyry guxW nUM) AwK ky ibAwn kry BI iks qrHW? ieh swry jIv (qW) qyrw hI ricAw hoieAw iek Kyl hY[
hryk jIv ivc qUM Awp hI boldw hYN, hryk jIv dI qUM Awp hI sMBwl krdw hYN (qUM hI krdw hYN) ijs ny ieh sMswr pYdw kIqw hY[
nwnk AwKdw hY ik (hy myry ipAwry mn! pRBU A`gy ieauN ArzoeI kr-) qUM sdw AphuMc hYN, (iksy jIv ny qyry guxW dw kdy) AMq nhIN l`Bw ]12]
(Awqmk AwnMd iek AYsw) AMimRq (hY ijs) nUM dyvqy mnu`K munI lok l`Bdy iPrdy hn, (pr) ieh AMimRq gurU qoN hI imldw hY[
ijs mnu`K au~qy gurU ny myhr kIqI aus ny (ieh) AMimRq pRwpq kr ilAw (ikauNik) aus ny sdw kwiem rihx vwlw pRBU Awpxy mn ivc itkw ilAw[
hy pRBU! swry jIA jMq qUM hI pYdw kIqy hn (qUM hI iehnW nUM pRyrdw hYN, qyrI pRyrnw nwl hI) keI jIv (gurU dw) dIdwr kr ky (aus dy) crn Cuhx AwauNdy hn,
siqgurU auhnW nUM ipAwrw l`gdw hY (siqgurU dI ikrpw nwl auhnW dw) l`b loB qy AhMkwr dUr ho jWdw hY[
nwnk AwKdw hY ik pRBU ijs mnu`K auqy pRsMn huMdw hY, aus mnu`K ny (Awqmk AwnMd-rUp) AMimRq gurU qoN pRwpq kr ilAw hY ]13]
(jyhVy suBwg bMdy Awqmk AwnMd mwxdy hn auhI Bgq hn qy auhnW) BgqW dI jIvn-jugqI (dunIAw dy lokW nwloN sdw) v`KrI huMdI hY,
(ieh p`kI g`l hY ik auhnW) BgqW dI jIvn-jugqI (hornW nwloN) v`KrI huMdI hY[ auh (bVy) AOKy rsqy auqy qurdy hn[
auh l`b loB AhMkwr qy mwieAw dI iqRSnw iqAwgdy hn qy bhuqw nhIN boldy (Bwv, AwpxI soBw nhIN krdy iPrdy)[
ies rsqy auqy qurnw (bVI AOKI Kyf hY ikauNik ieh rsqw) KMfy dI Dwr nwloN iqR`Kw hY qy vwl nwloN pqlw hY (ies auqoN if`gx dI BI sMBwvnw hr vyly bxI rihMdI hY ikauNik dunIAw vwlI vwsnw mn dI Afolqw nUM D`kw dy dyNdI hY)[
